				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{ENC}-\mathrm{plot}=2+\mathrm{s}+\left(\frac{29}{s^2+{\left(1+ s\right)}^2}\right) $$\end{document}ENC−plot=2+s+29s2+1+s2where s is the GC content at the third codon position, namely the GC3s.

